What do you love the most about SlamBall ?

Honestly when people ask me this question, they think I’m going to say “dunking on people” or “spending time in Vegas”. The truth is I loved being an inspiration to the kids. Being able to play the sport that you love and have kids full of excitement watching you play is truly a blessing. SlamBall has given me the platform to be a role model for the younger generation and I’m forever thankful. Of course I love dunking, hitting, and shooting, but nothing puts a smile on my face more than being able to sign a small autograph and make that young kid smile. Excited for the next season of @slamballofficial , so I can inspire more…
